  "name": "Wand of Continuation (4th-Level Spell)",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>This wand increases a spell's duration. Yellow embers spiral over its surface until the spell ends.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell; The activation takes <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> if the spell normally takes <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> to cast, or <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> if the spell normally takes <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span></p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> Once per day, plus overcharge</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You Cast the Spell, and its duration is increased by half.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply a casting of a spell of the appropriate level. The spell must have a casting time of <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> or <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> and a duration no less than 10 minutes and no greater than 1 hour.</p>"
    },
